Comment: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================MAIN==================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我还不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然手段有点强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是为了从坏人手中抢回胜君 这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,坏人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 坏人肯定盯上了胜君的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但已经不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔是才贺善治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是胜君父亲的弟弟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲拜托过我一定要照顾好你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,来 换了衣服多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鸣海哥哥 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好怕 这个大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,诱拐组的家伙凑了好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而且听说那里遍地陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,关于那件事 我自有打算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托某几位打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 摩托来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,从正面…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何这也太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么乱不乱来 我来吸引敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你丫的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,少嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我打
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,觉悟吧 走狗们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,少在那乱吠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不怕死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,置之死地而后生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有胆偶尔也能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,耍什么帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,包围起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个男人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加藤 鸣海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\i1}你去找小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小哥真的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个机会超乎想象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,杀手组上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 逃进傀儡门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,休想继续前进 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,阿紫花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这里交给我和旋转手臂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶 就交给那家伙开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,能那么顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,回来 旋转手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,救命 手套脱不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,让人看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那些家伙的目的是杀害少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,和这里诱拐少爷的家伙们结果上没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只会少一个敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多么冷漠的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是阿紫花也没法通过这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没有我上场的份 好空虚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 小姐 你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,自信满满的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了守护少爷而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而丑角也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,圣乔治之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,LES ARTS MARTIAUX
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗的艺术！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶 冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一口气冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 忘记我和泰奥高奇了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面的小姐 好戏才刚刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不合你的胃口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我已经饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,胜君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,想必你已经发觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多人盯上了你的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可是待在这里就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 做我的养子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个大叔是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为他说鸣海哥哥和白银是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不跑不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在走廊尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必须逃走 必须逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,高见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别以为那个小姐和我们一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们人偶师一族完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从小就在操纵人偶了 你却说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心少爷的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快点动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不要惹对方生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她拿着炸弹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,炸死你 泰奥高奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,丑角
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,居然把炸弹球全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你似乎从小就开始练习操纵人偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而我 从出生的一刻就是人偶师了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,胜 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在稍微教训你一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我接下来要怎么办 白银 鸣海哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才贺贞义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是爸爸的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么这里 会有我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我有话问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,操纵巨大的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不把人命当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 救少爷要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在姑且算是和这家伙联手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不摸清底细就没法放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,美… 美人说的比较对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们人偶师现在被称为黑贺一族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,追根溯源 是平安时代 在神社献上神乐人偶舞的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,简而言之就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 这是我的页
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:18.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs100\b1\be2\fay-0.2\move(646,922,646,-172)}胜\N是\N诱\N饵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1111B9&}胜是诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1111B9&}或者说是让不需要的人偶和人偶师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1111B9&}黑贺一族自爆的开关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是诱饵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么 什么意思 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,曾负责为神献上人偶舞的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要做这么危险的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,其实以前制造我们使用的人偶的 就是才贺家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,从前是黑贺一族花钱拜托对方制造人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在是才贺花大价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,请我们使用人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而且如小哥所知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,造出了兵器一样的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们来实验其性能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 如果能保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就事后再见吧 散开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当心 这里可是机关宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不知有什么陷阱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 发病了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,加藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1111B9&}如果我把财产留给胜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1111B9&}遗属们想必会雇佣黑贺一族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1111B9&}互相争夺胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1111B9&}这样黑贺一族就会分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1111B9&}用人偶自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1111B9&}胜是为此的诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 在这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,加藤 不用管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,放手 然后去救少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,连你都是人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,从昨天起就一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,每个家伙都不去挣扎乖乖死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,白银
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你没法守护胜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不珍惜自己生命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就不可能知道生命的沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 胜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要乖乖成为我的养子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔的养子 我才不要当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,胜 很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你等待的两人已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给你看看两人的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然后当我的养子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还发病了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且这不是犯规吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}眼泪什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痴痴看着女人 一边喘粗气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不就完全成变态了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我们从那里落下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的伤难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是我不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这次似乎轮到我让你先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个ZONAPHA病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快… 走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也能平息你的病症吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能笑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候笑才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧 我打从一开始就没指望让你笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,请再做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是为了保护我才受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须向你报恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你真死板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个女人不可能因为我的行为而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明这么担心胜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好恨在这里停步不前的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别管我先走啊 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会告诉你 你不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我来说个搞笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你要成为我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 笑不出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你先走…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那可真是不好笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么 病情控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反而是胸口…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 只是心跳加速吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我没法好好笑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还活着 两人都还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是鸣海哥哥受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 两个人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么能输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思啊 你说你是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对我说的话怀恨在心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对不住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我真是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道父母的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在法国的裘贝隆长大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在我记事时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,已经被教育操纵人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太硬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要我说多少遍才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,婆婆们总是重复着同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须把爱蕾诺这个名字和疼痛一起舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不 悲伤 喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,舍弃一切感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你要成为操纵人偶的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,爱蕾诺？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你的本名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那已经不是我的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,天生的人偶师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,背负使命而生的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是白银 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,使命？ 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,让土归土
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,人偶归于人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:19:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,把某人制造的自动人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,用悬丝人偶来破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这 这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道自己是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只是遵照命令一直在破坏人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,作为不会笑的 操纵人偶的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,说起笑容 胜 那家伙的笑容最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可是啊 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你的笑脸也很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,傻死了 人偶怎么可能做出刚才的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,给我好好听着 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不是什么人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 在那种地方很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔 我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要任叔叔摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你在胡思乱想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好怕 果然还是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,回来吧 胜 我不会再打你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先前我一直好孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是 有两人鼓励我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天也赶来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甚至不惜受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\i1}不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\i1}你会变强的 比我更强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}变强 变强 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来 你要成为我的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和先前一样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又会给他们俩添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我必须要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,给我适可而止吧 胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要做傻事 你想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:21:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我要杀掉 先前那个只会哭的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后 如果能活下来 活下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}变成随时都能笑得出来的我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让你随便过去的 阿紫花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 压过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才贺胜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 不是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔是要杀我的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我有话说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔由我来雇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 站在我这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}简直是另一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是充满求生欲的 野兽的眼睛
Comment: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================C-PART=================================================
Comment: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================ED=================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:19.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}舞い上がれマリオネット　美しく果て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:24.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}生きる価値　戦うしか私にはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:28.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}人を捨ててまで　この怒りは何故
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:34.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}君がいないと　もう笑うことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:40.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}悪いのは自分だと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:44.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}うまく笑えない　人形みたいだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:49.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誰かに操られているように　そんな気もして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:53.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}どうして生きてるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:22:58.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誰にもわかってもらえないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:03.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}思ってた痛みも　君が抱きしめてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:11.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}絡まる手足が解けてくみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}舞い上がれマリオネット　今なら届きそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:21.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}君と出会うまで私には何もなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:25.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}すべて賭けても　守りたいもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:32.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,400)}悲しい気持ちも　君が教えてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:19.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}起舞吧人偶 美丽的逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:24.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我生存的价值只有战斗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:28.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不惜舍弃做人 这份愤怒为何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:34.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}没有你在 我已经没法笑得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:40.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}本以为是自己不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:44.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就像不会笑的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:49.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}感觉像是被什么人操纵着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:53.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}为什么要活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:22:58.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}没有任何人理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:03.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}想到这里的那份心痛 都被你紧拥在怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:11.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}被束缚的手脚似乎解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}起舞吧人偶 现在感觉能送达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:21.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}和你相遇之前我一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:25.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使赌上一切 也要守护之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:32.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,400)}悲伤的感情 也是你教会了我
